@page "/"

<PageTitle>Conference App</PageTitle>

<h1>Conference Management System</h1>

<p>Welcome to the Conference App - manage presentations, questions, and ratings</p>

<div class="row mt-4">
    <div class="col-md-4">
        <div class="card">
            <div class="card-body">
                <h5 class="card-title">📊 Presentations</h5>
                <p class="card-text">Manage conference presentations, speakers, and schedules</p>
                <a href="/presentations" class="btn btn-primary">View Presentations</a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="col-md-4">
        <div class="card">
            <div class="card-body">
                <h5 class="card-title">❓ Questions</h5>
                <p class="card-text">View and answer attendee questions</p>
                <a href="/presentations" class="btn btn-primary">Manage Questions</a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="col-md-4">
        <div class="card">
            <div class="card-body">
                <h5 class="card-title">⭐ Ratings</h5>
                <p class="card-text">View attendee ratings and feedback</p>
                <a href="/presentations" class="btn btn-primary">View Ratings</a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

<div class="mt-5">
    <h3>About ConfApp</h3>
    <p>This application is built with Blazor and Entity Framework Core. It consists of:</p>
    <ul>
        <li><strong>ConfAPI</strong> - Admin interface for managing events (this app)</li>
        <li><strong>ConfMobileApp</strong> - Attendee interface for viewing and interacting with presentations</li>
        <li><strong>API Endpoints</strong> - RESTful API for data access</li>
    </ul>
</div>
